headline: Lululemon (LULU) Stock Is Up, What You Need To Know
summary: Shares of athletic apparel retailer Lululemon (NASDAQ:LULU) jumped 4.1% in the morning session after positive results from peer retailer Dollar General pointed to resilience in consumer spending. Dollar General raised its full-year guidance after its net sales for the third quarter rose 4.6% to $10.6 billion. The company noted that the sales increase was driven by improved customer traffic. headline: 2 Profitable Stocks to Own for Decades and 1 That Underwhelm
summary: Not all profitable companies are built to last - some rely on outdated models or unsustainable advantages. Just because a business is in the green today doesn’t mean it will thrive tomorrow.
